A couple of hints for those of you who are having trouble with the consistancy of the cookies. 1. Never beat the butter and sugar--just mix until blended. Excessive beating increases the flour requirement. 2. Always chill cookie dough after mixing before baking. 3. Also, I increased the flour from 1 cup to 1 and 1/4 cup.

